               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280110-89-cd446" type="crimeDate">10th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-89-off445 t18280110-89-cd446"></join>, 4 lbs. of cheese, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280110-89-victim631" type="victimName">
                  Jacob 
                  Townsend
               <interp inst="t18280110-89-victim631" type="surname" value="Townsend"></interp>
